    "en": {
      "title": "The commercial division cup goes to Ratnavali",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ishini Neha Amararatne, a student of Gampaha Ratnawali Balika Vidyalaya, has succeeded in securing the first position in the island in the commercial section of the 2021 General Certificate of Studies (Higher Level) examination.",
        "She appeared for the exam in English medium and secured the first position in the commerce section.",
        "In addition to this, the principal Mrs. Hema Jayavaradhana said that a student of Ratnavali girl has managed to get the second place in the island in the biology section."
      ],
